{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "希里丝（铳士Ver.） 第4话 传承至未来的传统",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "这里就是瓦尔斯加德啊……\\n好宽阔的城市啊！\\n而且还很热闹！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "是的，因为瓦尔斯加德\\n是北大陆屈指可数的，\\n贸易都市……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "听说是，融合了很多文明，\\n逐渐发展起来的，城市。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "融合文明发展起来的城市！\\n看来能学到不少文化呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "好！卢卡哥哥，诺艾尔！\\n我们这就去转转吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "啊，希里丝，那边是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "咦？这条路是怎么回事，\\n氛围和正街上不一样……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "这、这里是，贫民区……\\n治安也不太好，还是别……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "贫民区？这么发达的城市\\n还有很多穷人吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "是的……瓦尔斯加德的确是\\n靠吸收生产力更先进的异文化\\n发展起来的城市，但是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "吸收文化快也就意味着\\n自古以来的那些文化……\\n也就是传统，会遭到淘汰……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "每当有更高效的文化传入，\\n依靠人力的事物就会慢慢减少，\\n结果……就是失业的人也很多。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "而且，也不是所有人\\n都能适应新文化……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "这样啊……接受文化\\n也很不容易呢……嗯？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "希里丝，你怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "啊，嗯，那家店……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "银饰？不对，那是……\\n罗卡族的钢铁饰品！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "好厉害！都好酷啊！\\n这全是大叔你做的？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "哼……如果你\\n是来冷嘲热讽的，就请回吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "诶？我没有嘲讽啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "你这个森隐族就别胡说了。\\n你们讨厌钢铁，\\n怎么会懂钢铁饰品的好。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "哼！我说大叔！\\n这我可不能当没听见！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "我是真的觉得你的饰品很酷！\\n别那么说啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "是吗是吗。那就好。\\n我知道了所以你赶紧走吧，\\n小兔子。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "什么！真让人来气！\\n既然你都说到了那个份上……\\n我也要你见识一下我的诚意！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "所以大叔，你就……\\n教我做钢铁饰品吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡&诺艾尔",
            "context": "诶！?",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "你、你在说什么呢。\\n你不是过路旅客吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "我能稍微逗留一阵子！\\n对吧，诺艾尔！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "诶，啊，是的……\\n我们预计在这里，\\n逗留5天左右……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "那就没问题了！\\n而且我正在学习不同的文化。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "我学东西很快的，\\n你就教教我罗卡族的技术嘛！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "学得快？\\n嚯……你还真敢说大话啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "好，那就试试吧。\\n看森隐族的柔弱小姑娘\\n到底能不能行……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "哈啊、哈啊……没、没想到\\n要自己来挖掘矿山！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "小兔子，已经要放弃了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "可恶！还早着呢！\\n看我给你飞快向前挖！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "听好了，要趁烧红的时候\\n一口气打成型。\\n会有火星四溅，要忍住！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "哇！哇啊！好烫！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "呜呜……\\n烧伤……肌肉酸痛……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "喂，不是说了要日出之前起床吗？\\n工匠的一天可是开始得很早的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "我、我知道！\\n我一定要打出让你服气的饰品，\\n摆在那家店里！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "哈哈……有力气说大话\\n还不如快点到工坊来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "呼……\\n做好……了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "拿来，我看看成色。\\n嗯……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "不赖，虽然还很粗糙，\\n不过比想象中好。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "做得不错，\\n最后一天终于有模样了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "真的吗？\\n太、太、太好了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "哈，你做的饰品\\n就拿走当纪念吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "诶？可以吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "嗯，留着当回忆吧，毕竟……\\n它是这间工坊打造的\\n最后一件东西了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "这话是什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "……\\n我的店，要关门了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "关门……\\n是说不再卖货了吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "嗯，很早以前就决定了。\\n我以为你很快就会示弱，\\n所以才没说。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "怎么会！钢铁饰品不是\\n罗卡族宝贵的传统工艺吗？\\n为什么要放弃啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "是啊，的确是很宝贵的文化，\\n我也不是要放弃，\\n只是改变一下形式。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "形式？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "你看这个……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "这是……钢铁饰品，\\n店主你做的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "不……不对。\\n这饰品没有你做的那种感觉……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "那是自然。\\n毕竟这不是手工打造的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "不是手工打造的？\\n那是怎么做出来的？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "用别的罗卡村落的技术，\\n名叫模具制法，\\n是最近传入这座城市的流行技术。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "流行的技术？\\n啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "这里接受文化很快，相对地，\\n舍弃古老文化的习俗也根深蒂固，\\n失业的人，也很多……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "难道，钢铁饰品的文化……\\n这种制法要改变了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "是啊，模具制法更方便量产，\\n城市也会更富裕，\\n所以他们让我放弃手工打造。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "但、但是……\\n店主你对手工打造有追求吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "有。不过，我也得生活。\\n所以我不干了，\\n以后就去工厂干活。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "先不说这些了。只是……\\n手工制法消失会很可惜。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "店主……\\n不，不会消失的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "著名饰品工匠",
            "context": "希里丝？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "的确，模具制法更便宜\\n还能量产，也许一开始\\n大家都会倒向那边。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "不过，他们总有一天会发现，\\n手工制法有手工制法的优点！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "毕竟，我都能看出来\\n这是不是你打的饰品！\\n也更喜欢你打的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120105_01"
            ],
